title: The Best Scallion Pancake Recipe Turns into Breakfast Tacos — You Can Do This!
description:
Clifford Endo is back with You Can Do This! Kicking off this season, Endo will show you how to make Bacon-Filled Scallion Pancake Breakfast Tacos and, like, you can totally do this at home!  Share it with a loved one or a.... loved one, they'll thank you. Some assembly required, but it is definitely worth it. You Can Do This!

Eater is the one-stop-shop for food and restaurant obsessives across the country. With features, explainers, animations, recipes, and more — it’s the most indulgent food content around. So get hungry.
